</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the counter of missing pulses is not enough to give a position fault, it can result in the line counter error. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the error occurs with the printhead carriage on, or close to the platen, this is the cause.
</p><p class="- topic/p ">In case the encoder strip is dirty or damaged, it can result in missing pulses.
</p><p class="- topic/p ">When the counter of missing pulses is not enough to give a position fault, it can result in the line counter error.
